            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>bacon frijoles charros </strong>with the<strong> cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Dollop over your <strong>soured cream</strong> and the <strong>lime salsa </strong>and garnish with<strong> reserved coriander leaves </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
